title: A’s look for reasons behind disappointing season
text:
Photo: Elaine Thompson, Associated Press A’s players watch the final out in the ninth inning of Oakland’s 3-2 loss to Seattle on the final day of the regular season. A’s players watch the final out in the ninth inning of...
SEATTLE — With an eminently disappointing season in the books, the A’s look back at what went wrong: lots of injuries, natch. An unreliable bullpen. A shaky defense.
